{
  "stem": "1530.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they were gone, maybe a half an hour, Izabel and I said, well, let's go into this house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't know where [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Chicha ?] is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We go in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were already two Polish women in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we say, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Chicha-- ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish women.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who also, I guess, got out of the line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chicha ?] is-- we call her name, and she was in the attic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we go up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, you know, there are no people here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The smoke is still going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They must have just evacuated this village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Smart as anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't think in those terms, because I was normal, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she figured it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we're in a home that has everything in it, all the food that you ever saw in your life, no people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then when we were able to go out of the house, we saw the whole village is totally evacuated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans pushed the people ahead, that they shouldn't be caught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left all the food and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think they had pasta.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had everything from all over the world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I saw chickens and a duck and a goose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, my little frightened self, go out and found something, and I killed one of the-- goose or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I my made chicken soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got so sick from it because it had fat in it, and we couldn't digest anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very thin anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we had this diarrhea, we just became really very sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you-- you were in-- you continued to stay in this house?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
